---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'What does Easel cost?',
    a: "Provisioning and hosting an Easel site is completely free. You should expect to pay around $20 a year at max for a custom domain, if you aren't already.",
  },
  {
    q: 'What accounts do I need?',
    a: "You'll need to create a free GitHub and Netlify account to provision an Easel site. GitHub hosts the code for your Easel site, while Netlify serves it as a website.",
  },
  {
    q: 'What prior coding knowledge do I need?',
    a: "None! Easel uses a simple sitebuilder, and you'll never need to interact with the code that makes your site work.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I use a custom domain?',
    a: 'Absolutely! Custom domains are free with Netlify.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What kind of work can I show?',
    a: "Anything visual! Easel is built around image galleries, so it's a great fit for illustrators, photographers, painters, designers, and more.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I change how my site looks?',
    a: "Yes! You can adjust colors, fonts, and layout right from the sitebuilder, no code required.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Who owns my site and content?',
    a: "You do, fully. Your site lives on your own GitHub and Netlify accounts, so it stays online whether or not you keep using Easel.",
  },
  {
    q: 'I have an unanswered question or idea for a feature!',
    a: 'Shoot me an email at easel@rosematcha.com.',
  },
];
---

<section class="section faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Questions</p>
    <h2>You should know&hellip;</h2>
    <div class="faq__list">
      {faqs.map((item) => (
        <details class="faq__item">
          <summary>{item.q}</summary>
          <p>{item.a}</p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq__list {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    max-width: 760px;
  }
  .faq__item {
    border: var(--border);
    background: var(--c-white);
  }
  .faq__item summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .faq__item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq__item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--c-blue);
  }
  .faq__item[open] summary::after { content: '\2013'; }
  .faq__item p {
    padding: 0 var(--space-4) var(--space-4);
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--c-stone);
  }
</style>
